> can you try to use a model which vllm-omni supports: Qwen3-Omni, Qwen3-tts or diffusion models as a good example to demonstrate the problem? Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct will be served with vllm alone.

@hsliuustc0106 Thanks — that's a good point. I've redone the evidence on Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B, a genuine two-stage Qwen-family pipeline (talker → code2wav) that vLLM can't serve standalone, and updated the issue body accordingly.

If the approach looks good, I'll start submitting the PRs incrementally. Anything else you'd like adjusted first?
